text: Beavis and Butt-Head Do the Universe is a 2022 American adult animated comedy movie. It was directed by Jim Reardon and written by Mike Judge and Scott Hemming. == Cast == == Release == The movie was released on December 16, 2022, on Paramount Pictures. == References == == Other websites == * Category:2020s English-language movies Category:2022 animated movies Category:American satirical movies Category:2022 comedy movies Category:American animated movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies set in Texas
